---
layout: base.njk
title: Le Signal
description: "The Forgotten Industries signal record: field notes, updates, observations, reports, and dispatches."
permalink: /signal/index.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
{% set reports = archive.fieldLogs | fieldLogsNewest %}
<section class="section-landing-hero">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">LE SIGNAL / THE AUTHORED RECORD</p>
    <h1>Le Signal</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Everything transmitted. Everything observed.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="signal-ticker-band" aria-labelledby="signal-ticker-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="signal-ticker-header">
      <p class="section-label">Current transmissions</p>
      <h2 id="signal-ticker-heading" class="sr-only">Recent signal activity</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="signal-ticker" role="list" aria-label="Recent signal activity">
      {% if fieldnotes.length %}
      {% for note in fieldnotes %}
      {% if loop.index <= 4 %}
      <a class="signal-ticker-item" role="listitem" href="{{ note.url }}" data-track="outbound-field-note">
        <span>En Direct / {{ note.createdAt | readableDate }}</span>
        <strong>{{ note.text | escape }}</strong>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      {% endif %}
      {% for report in reports %}
      {% if loop.index <= 4 %}
      <a class="signal-ticker-item" role="listitem" href="/field-logs/{{ report.slug }}/">
        <span>ATLAS / {{ report.date | replace('-', '.') | replace('-', '.') }}</span>
        <strong>{{ report.title }}</strong>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-directory" aria-labelledby="signal-directory-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">Three active channels</p>
    <h2 id="signal-directory-heading">Signals, separated by source.</h2>
    <div class="directory-grid plate-card-grid signal-directory-grid">
      <a href="/atlas/">
        <span>01 / {{ archive.fieldLogs | countLabel("report", "reports") }}</span>
        <h3>ATLAS Reports</h3>
        <p>AI-assisted end-of-day debriefs: evidence, decisions, unresolved questions, and next actions.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/field-logs/">
        <span>02 / {{ archive.voiceLogs | countLabel("recording", "recordings") }}</span>
        <h3>Field Logs</h3>
        <p>Original voice records from the portable recorder. The empty intake template is live and ready.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/en-direct/">
        <span>03 / {{ fieldnotes | countLabel("dispatch", "dispatches") }}</span>
        <h3>En Direct</h3>
        <p>The continuous shortform signal imported from Bluesky at build time.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
